room_title: Escape room "Lost In Time" by Mastermind Escape Games in Chicago
review: Lost time room was outstanding! There were some really clever puzzles, gizmos, and things to interact with. So glad our group went.

room_title: Escape room "Lost In Time" by Mastermind Escape Games in Chicago
review: We had the best time! We did the Lost in Time room. There were some tricky clues and puzzles to figure out but we managed to escape with a little over 3 minutes to spare. Can't wait to go on another adventure. The staff were super too!

room_title: Escape room "Lost In Time" by Mastermind Escape Games in Chicago
review: This was our second visit. We made it through "Lost In Time" and had a lot of fun. We definitely recommend Mastermind!
